import React, {Component} from "react" import { Route,Link,Redirect,withRouter } from "react-router-dom"; import DashBoard from './dashboard.js' class LoginForm extends Component{ constructor(){ super(); this.state = { email: "", password:"", loggedIn: false, staus:"" } this.changehandler = this.changehandler.bind(this) this.submithandler = this.submithandler.bind(this) } async submithandler(event){ event.preventDefault(); await fetch('http://localhost:4000/login',{ method: 'post', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'accept': "application/json"}, body: JSON.stringify({ "email":this.state.email, "password":this.state.password, }) }).then(res=>res.json()).then((res=>localStorage.setItem('tok',res.token))) } changehandler = name => event => { this.setState({ [name]: event.target.value }) } render(){ return(
Login V20 {this.state.staus} {localStorage.getItem('tok')}

Account Login
Email Address
Password
) } } export default withRouter(LoginForm)
